summary: I just had the saddest thought. I remember marvel saying the uncle Ben was there during the battle in New York and it got me...
body: I just had the saddest thought. I remember marvel saying the uncle Ben was there during the battle in New York and it got me wondering…what if iron man was the one who saved uncle Ben when that happened? What if THAT turns out to be why Peter admires him so much? That makes everything even more heartbreaking because Peter would later fail to save his uncle. He wants to be like Tony because Tony didn’t let his uncle die.

summary: would you help me to carry the stone? - sturwurstrash - Spider-Man: Homecoming (2017) [Archive of Our Own]
title: would you help me to carry the stone? - sturwurstrash - Spider-Man: Homecoming (2017) [Archive of Our Own]
excerpt: An Archive of Our Own, a project of the Organization for Transformative Works
description:
Part 2 of Being Alive (is different than living)

He thought back to that day in the car, when he finally, tearfully, told May that he needed help. It wasn’t that long ago, only a month or so, but Peter couldn’t help but feel he was falling harder and faster than ever. That he was an atomic missile within inches of hitting its target. Ready to explode on impact. As if one little thing would cause him to explode and poison the entire city with radiation. They were the unlucky ones. The ones who survived the impact. Just like he was unlucky in so many ways.
–
Peter is struggling in a world post-snap. It doesn’t help that Tony is struggling too.

I know its been like 3 months, but pt. 2 is finally here! I’m continuing my original plans for this series, which makes it completely AU and not compliant with Endgame at all. I guess you could say this series has become my version of a fix-it! I hope you will all enjoy!

summary: I saw your trans! Peter fanfic ideas and all I gotta say is why are you going to transwash him?
question: I saw your trans! Peter fanfic ideas and all I gotta say is why are you going to transwash him?
answer:
T…. Transwash?

Okay, mate, you see, I am a trans man. This is a harmless au/headcanon that literal tens of thousands of trans people indulge in because positive representation is key to having good self esteem and not hating yourself.

If you happen to be a poc or LGBT, you would understand this and understand what representation means to us. But from your response, I’m unsure.

We don’t get superheros that look like us. We don’t even get mainstream characters that look like us.

We’re just having fun by making do with what we got.

Hey everyone :DJAM HERE!

A gift for a classmate and also because this movie is great! It’s just amazing in general I loved the music (heck I’m not much into rapping but this movie gave me some good soundtrack), and the animation is outstanding (as an artist it’s like a gift nicely wrapped in comic book themed paper which I find comic book styles fun and unique here)

I’ve been wanting to draw something from this movie now I have an excuse to draw Miles 😂

Watch the movie it’s amazing

Art by me
